You've always liked how hourglasses looked, but you can't flip this one by yourself.
Sometimes Papa will flip this one for you when you ask, but even he seems to struggle with its weight.
It's probably more of a decoration than anything that can be of actual practical use.
The scenario of you pulling this off the table only for the hourglass to crush you to death would surely make for an interesting ending.
Fortunately (or unfortunately) there is no way for you to make this even budge.
